title: The Immortal Emperor Luo Wuji has returned
alternative_titles: The Immortal Emperor Luo Wuji has returned
summary: “Disciples and brothers betrayed one after another, and a generation of immortals fell. Though the body is dead, the soul is immortal! And with the most precious “Supreme Emperor’s Scripture” to reverse the cause and effect, return to the earth, break the karmic barrier, and cast the divine personality again! This life will make the name of “Wuji” above the sun and moon! 仙尊洛无极, The Immortal Emperor Luo Wuji has returned, Immortal Emperor Luo Wuji, Deity Luo Wu Ji
